OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772460677
OL,3,CMan denies criminal damage after
OL,4,CWinston Churchill statue defaced with
OL,5,Cgraffiti
OL,7,FThe Metropolitan Police said Caspar
OL,8,FSan Giorgio, of no fixed address, was
OL,9,Farrested shortly after 4am on Friday
OL,10,Ffollowing the incident and was charged
OL,11,Fwith criminal damage in the early
OL,12,Fhours of Saturday.
OL,14,FOn Monday morning, the 38-year-old
OL,15,Fappeared at Westminster Magistrates'
OL,16,FCourt wearing a grey T-shirt and
OL,17,Fjoggers.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/4
