PN,40103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772460677
OL,3,CMan denies criminal damage after
OL,4,CWinston Churchill statue defaced with
OL,5,Cgraffiti
OL,7,FWhen asked to confirm his name, he
OL,8,Fsaid it is Olax Outis, but Katie
OL,9,FMcFadden, defending, added it is
OL,10,FCaspar San Giorgio on his passport,
OL,11,Fand he pleaded not guilty.
OL,13,FHe is accused of damaging the statue
OL,14,Fto the value of #11,970, the court
OL,15,Fheard.
OL,17,FHe was remanded into custody by Judge
OL,18,FCaroline Jackson, who told him he will
OL,19,Fnext appear at Southwark Crown Court
OL,20,Fon March 30.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/4
