OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772460677
OL,3,CMan denies criminal damage after
OL,4,CWinston Churchill statue defaced with
OL,5,Cgraffiti
OL,7,FDutch group Free The Filton 24 claimed
OL,8,Fresponsibility for the action on
OL,9,FFriday morning, posting a video on
OL,10,FInstagram appearing to show the
OL,11,Fincident in progress.
OL,13,FFree The Filton 24 defines itself as a
OL,14,Fgroup of "family and friends" of the
OL,15,F24 Palestine Action activists who were
OL,16,Fcharged over a break-in at one of
OL,17,FIsrael-based defence firm Elbit's UK
OL,18,Fsites in 2024.
